# Copy to `.env` and fill in. All are optional — each feature degrades
# gracefully (hides itself / shows 0) when its vars are absent.

# --- Visitor counter (Upstash Redis) ---------------------------------------
# Powers ONLY the footer "👀 N visitors" count: a Redis set of fingerprint IDs
# (SADD to add, SCARD to count). Create a free serverless DB at
# https://console.upstash.com → Redis → "REST API" tab.
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=

# --- GitHub (Sponsors + star counts) ---------------------------------------
# Classic Personal Access Token, scope: read:user. Powers the Sponsors section
# (GitHub Sponsors) and lifts the API rate limit for project star counts.
# Create one: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=
